com.b2international.commons.status

Class Statuses

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.b2international.commons.status.Statuses

  • public final class Statuses
extends Object
    Common methods and functions to work with IStatus, SerializableStatus and SerializableMultiStatus instances much more easily.

    3.2
